Package: gkwreg2
Title: Generalized Kumaraswamy Regression Models for Bounded Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "JosÃ© Evandeilton",
                    family = "Lopes",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "evandeilton@gmail.com",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-5887-4084")))
Description: Provides regression modeling for data bounded in (0,1) using the 
    Generalized Kumaraswamy distribution family. Implements maximum likelihood 
    estimation via RcppArmadillo with analytical gradients from the gkwdist package.
    Supports seven distribution families: GKw (5 parameters), BKw (4), KKw (4), 
    EKw (3), McDonald/MC (3), Kw (2), and Beta (2). Features extended formula 
    syntax for specifying different covariates per parameter.
